  "name": "RPlog_Deep_Space_Skirmish",
  "title": "Deep Space Skirmish",
  "summary": "A routine New Republic patrol led by Lance 'Wildman' Corbet in Rogue Two, flanked by the disgruntled A-wing pilot Marl 'Gambit' and another Falcon, stumbles upon a Sith ambush after a Corellian Corvette is destroyed in a brilliant flash. Darth Malign himself, flying a heavily modified X-wing, and his apprentice Vectus in a souped-up Z-95 engage the patrol. Wildman, recognizing his old foe, duels Malign in a tense, evenly fought dogfight while Gambit and Vectus trade fire in a separate standstill. Outmatched and with his shields failing, Wildman orders Gambit to jump out and summon reinforcements, choosing to hold the Sith as long as he can. Bored once the A-wings flee and disinclined to finish the lone X-wing himself, Malign breaks off and orders his fighters to regroup near Ord Grovner, leaving Wildman to bug out into hyperspace as the inconclusive skirmish ends.",
